Horde AI Companion Invite
    Events
        Unit - A unit Starts the effect of an ability
    Conditions
        (Ability being cast) Equal to Invite Companion 
        ((Target unit of ability being cast) is Summoned) Not equal to True
        ((Target unit of ability being cast) is an illusion) Not equal to True
    Actions
        -------- --------- CHECK If invitable --------
        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
            If - Conditions
                (Target unit of ability being cast) Equal to Shadowclaw
            Then - Actions
                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                    If - Conditions
                        (Number of units in TamedUnits) Greater than or equal to 1
                    Then - Actions
                        -------- More than 1 beast tamed already --------
                        Game - Display to (All players) the text: You already have a ...
                        Skip remaining actions
                    Else - Actions
                        Sound - Play Rescue <gen>
                        Unit - Change ownership of Shadowclaw to Player 19 (Mint) and Retain color
                        Unit Group - Add Shadowclaw to TamedUnits
                        Unit Group - Add Shadowclaw to CompanionFocusNazgrek
                        Unit - Make Shadowclaw Vulnerable
                        Set VariableSet TamedUnit = Shadowclaw
                        -------- UNIT HIDER --------
                        Set VariableSet UnitHider_ReferenceUnits[(Custom value of Shadowclaw)] = Shadowclaw
                        Unit Group - Add Shadowclaw to UnitHider_ReferenceGroup
                        -------- Experience --------
                        Custom script:   call UnitExperience_DisableXP(udg_TamedUnit, false)
                        -------- Multiboard --------
                        -------- Reset values --------
                        Set VariableSet TamedUnitKillCount = 0
                        Set VariableSet TamedUnitDeathCount = 0
                        Trigger - Run MultiboardUpdate Add Tamed <gen> (ignoring conditions)
                        Skip remaining actions
            Else - Actions
        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
            If - Conditions
                Or - Any (Conditions) are true
                    Conditions
                        (Unit-type of (Target unit of ability being cast)) Equal to Warlock (Companion)
                        (Unit-type of (Target unit of ability being cast)) Equal to Rogue (Companion)
                        (Unit-type of (Target unit of ability being cast)) Equal to Tauren Warrior (Companion)
                        (Unit-type of (Target unit of ability being cast)) Equal to Restoration Shaman (Companion)
                        (Unit-type of (Target unit of ability being cast)) Equal to Engineer
                        (Unit-type of (Target unit of ability being cast)) Equal to Engineer (Shredder)
                        (Unit-type of (Target unit of ability being cast)) Equal to Paladin (Companion)
            Then - Actions
                -------- CHECK reputation of the unit's Faction --------
                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                    If - Conditions
                        ((Target unit of ability being cast) belongs to an enemy of (Owner of (Casting unit)).) Equal to False
                    Then - Actions
                        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                            If - Conditions
                                (Number of units in Companion_Group) Less than Companion_GroupSize
                            Then - Actions
                                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                                    If - Conditions
                                        (Hero level of (Target unit of ability being cast)) Less than or equal to ((Hero level of Nazgrek) + 5)
                                    Then - Actions
                                        Sound - Play Rescue <gen>
                                        Unit Group - Add (Target unit of ability being cast) to Companion_Group
                                        Unit Group - Add (Target unit of ability being cast) to CompanionFocusNazgrek
                                        Unit - Change ownership of (Target unit of ability being cast) to Player 19 (Mint) and Change color
                                        Game - Display to (All players) the text: ((Proper name of (Target unit of ability being cast)) +  has joined the party!)
                                        Set VariableSet CompanionCount = (CompanionCount + 1)
                                        Set VariableSet CompanionUnit[CompanionCount] = (Target unit of ability being cast)
                                        Set VariableSet CompanionIndex[(Custom value of (Target unit of ability being cast))] = CompanionCount
                                        Game - Display to (All players) the text: (debug companionCount value:  + (String(CompanionCount)))
                                        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                                            If - Conditions
                                                (Target unit of ability being cast) Equal to NPC_Horde_AI_Rogue
                                            Then - Actions
                                                Set VariableSet CompanionIcon[CompanionCount] = ReplaceableTextures\CommandButtons\BTNHeroBlademaster.blp
                                                -------- CHAT --------
                                                Trigger - Run Horde NPC Chat Greet Rogue <gen> (checking conditions)
                                            Else - Actions
                                                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                                                    If - Conditions
                                                        (Target unit of ability being cast) Equal to NPC_Horde_AI_Warlock
                                                    Then - Actions
                                                        Set VariableSet CompanionIcon[CompanionCount] = ReplaceableTextures\CommandButtons\BTNChaosWarlockGreen.blp
                                                        -------- CHAT --------
                                                        Trigger - Run Horde NPC Chat Greet Warlock <gen> (checking conditions)
                                                    Else - Actions
                                                        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                                                            If - Conditions
                                                                (Target unit of ability being cast) Equal to NPC_Horde_AI_Shaman
                                                            Then - Actions
                                                                Set VariableSet CompanionIcon[CompanionCount] = ReplaceableTextures\CommandButtons\BTNShaman.blp
                                                                -------- CHAT --------
                                                                Trigger - Run Horde NPC Chat Greet Restoshaman <gen> (checking conditions)
                                                            Else - Actions
                                                                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                                                                    If - Conditions
                                                                        (Target unit of ability being cast) Equal to NPC_Horde_AI_Warrior
                                                                    Then - Actions
                                                                        Set VariableSet CompanionIcon[CompanionCount] = ReplaceableTextures\CommandButtons\BTNHeroTaurenChieftain.blp
                                                                        -------- CHAT --------
                                                                        Trigger - Run Horde NPC Chat Greet Warrior <gen> (checking conditions)
                                                                    Else - Actions
                                                                        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                                                                            If - Conditions
                                                                                (Target unit of ability being cast) Equal to NPC_Neutral_Engineer
                                                                            Then - Actions
                                                                                Set VariableSet CompanionIcon[CompanionCount] = ReplaceableTextures\CommandButtons\BTNHeroTinker.blp
                                                                                -------- CHAT --------
                                                                                Trigger - Run Horde NPC Chat Greet Engineer <gen> (checking conditions)
                                                                            Else - Actions
                                                                                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                                                                                    If - Conditions
                                                                                        (Target unit of ability being cast) Equal to NPC_Riverbane_Paladin
                                                                                    Then - Actions
                                                                                        Set VariableSet CompanionIcon[CompanionCount] = ReplaceableTextures\CommandButtons\BTNHeroPaladin.blp
                                                                                        -------- CHAT --------
                                                                                        Trigger - Run Horde NPC Chat Greet Paladin <gen> (checking conditions)
                                                                                    Else - Actions
                                        Trigger - Run MultiboardUpdate Add Companion <gen> (checking conditions)
                                    Else - Actions
                                        Game - Display to (All players) the text: The target's level ...
                            Else - Actions
                                Game - Display to (All players) the text: |cFFFF0000Error: |r...
                    Else - Actions
                        Game - Display to (All players) the text: |cFFFF0000Error|r|c...
            Else - Actions
                Game - Display to (All players) the text: |cFFFF0000Error|r|c...
